**Android mentorship v2.0**
Task 2
Improvements :

 -Implementation of a splash screen


- The First Activity should be a dashboard  which shows the current highscore, the play and the quit game  button which should lead to the second activity

 -The Second Activity should be a screen which requires the user to select difficulty
        Easy - 3 colors
   		Medium - 6 colors
   		Hard - 10 colors
   		the user choice of difficulty will determine the amount of views in the next activity which has the game playing logic

 - at the end of each gameplay there should have an interface that indicates the end of the game , the result and 2 buttons  one to play again and one to quit.






